p://dbpedia.org/resource/Jan_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jan_Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 544, \"end\": 553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999999463398, \"rank\": 5.3877235572672214e-11, \"text\": \"Hollywood\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 563, \"end\": 573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PHOTO\", \"from\": 459, \"to\": 464}, {\"ngram\": \"05:43 AM\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 539}, {\"ngram\": \"a skyscraper\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 593}, {\"ngram\": \"a motorcycle\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 614}, {\"ngram\": \"a cliff\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 626}, {\"ngram\": \"his ankle\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 647}, {\"ngram\": \"one building\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 673}, {\"ngram\": \"another\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 684}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And now the 62-year-old actor, who often performs his own death-defying stunts in action movies such as the Mission: Impossible film series (1996 to present) and Top Gun: Maverick (2022), will take on his most high-profile feat yet: closing the Paris Olympics by rappelling off the roof of the Stade de France - the host country's national stadium.\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 1039, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 62-year-old actor\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 720}, {\"ngram\": \"his own death-defying stunts\", \"from\": 741, \"to\": 769}, {\"ngram\": \"action movies\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 786}, {\"ngram\": \"the Mission\", \"from\": 795, \"to\": 806}, {\"ngram\": \"Impossible film series\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 830}, {\"ngra